{"tid":1984413,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【自古以來⋯】香港地名嘅百越來源，粵、越一脈相承","createTime":"2020-04-22T12:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T13:14:37.000Z","uid":276716,"like":74,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fb6aedcaa7ac291bf6f570c012cc87f5273230","tid":1984413,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"香港地名，我哋知道有啲係由英語音譯，好似佐敦、堅尼地城咁。<br />\n<br />\n但其實所謂嘅中文地名當中，有好多百越元素，只係以漢字音譯過嚟。原因係香港自古以來係百越先民嘅土地，不過佢哋冇留低文字紀錄，部分又接受咗漢化生活，於是乎今日我哋只可以估估下，推敲出先民留低嘅足跡。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>九龍</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n根據網絡流傳嘅版本，八座山脈，加埋真龍天子宋帝昺，就謂之九龍。呢個咁中華膠到無倫嘅故事，真係駁都費事。我就由百越角度睇吓點解釋呢個名。<br />\n<br />\n壯語係古百越語嘅後裔，rugnh 解山間嘅平地，常見於地名，漢字通常音譯為龍、弄、峒、隴。Gyo，壯語解「多」。九龍嘅百越語可能就係gyo rungh， 即係好多山之間平地，漢字音譯為九龍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D17LTrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD17LTrf.jpg&h=1389c866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>元朗，塱原</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n朗，或塱，係粵地常見地名。壯語lengz，平地咁解。元朗以良田聞名，係香港少有嘅大片平原。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>白臘灣</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n壯語lak，解崩塌處。至於「白」，係好常見嘅地名，來自bak， 解作「口」，漢字通常音譯為白、百、博、薄。Bak Lak，「崩塌嘅口」。睇下白臘灣啲相，唔多解釋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3QQ4yp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3QQ4yp.jpg&h=74f93249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdOGrML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdOGrML.jpg&h=f2431499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>薄扶林</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n薄即係口，上面講咗。<br />\n扶，係標示方位<br />\n林，音譯自Raemx，水咁解<br />\n<br />\n舊時港島西部山溪滙集於薄扶林瀑布，英國人都有記載佢哋船員喺處攞水飲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51Y7nkb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51Y7nkb.jpg&h=837118d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>索罟灣</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n索罟灣位於南丫島，根據島上嘅古蹟，新石器時代已經有人住。<br />\n<br />\n壯語 Sokruz，碼頭咁解。越人出名善於行舟，先秦嘅漢文典籍都有記載。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNdjdrY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNdjdrY.jpg&h=ac867160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>石排灣</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n香港好多叫「排」嘅地方，好似石排灣、七星排、劏人排。粵地漁民一般叫礁石做「排」，壯語中vai解做阻擋水嘅壩體。下圖係劏人排。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqrdhTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqrdhTQ.jpg&h=7f7022f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>果欄</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n壯語laeng，屋企咁解。粵語嘅「埋欄」就保留咗呢個意思。但係一般用語入面，「欄」收窄為動物或死物嘅居所，例如豬欄、果欄。"},{"pid":"5c82c2a614a11e89a6b93f0a105960b0cd330d42","tid":1984413,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"e3d183af859216e694e50a3cb96d2534cc55e616","tid":1984413,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3266e63d21c2ddb9b6f72b730ad79d828f377c6","tid":1984413,"uid":92442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f743e2ea0bf5bb28e0610a654d7ec799c2195ba9","tid":1984413,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"Spln"},{"pid":"bda751eb2cccc1373537d11f665ed97dc7182d89","tid":1984413,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:47:40.000Z","msg":"本土歷史及文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">香 港 國 寶 ： 許冠傑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973620</a></div>"},{"pid":"d9a20a98487ca433da150cf9d628284105eb49c6","tid":1984413,"uid":33612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4120fdcce554d5c4391ed2586f2618f2e5108817","tid":1984413,"uid":218,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"學到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路覺得索罟灣唔似中文或者英文"},{"pid":"d0dc43352ecb4745d87e95ce6a929bd1801a0f93","tid":1984413,"uid":263197,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"有冇reference推介"},{"pid":"1581afc93a1978a0220ee991b616909ce9576b96","tid":1984413,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7880337e0c6fa18e8f33ce6e754bd4f7caef4fe7","tid":1984413,"uid":66399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"推  真係長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091058249b747a2461e33c0aaf69120d6a1b773a","tid":1984413,"uid":103315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"音節點查呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acfb2fc6df2bd880dae4a23a22f627ded4bcfab","tid":1984413,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"g持本土考古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eafb291d9475f5a18b0223f3afde0551d07d3d","tid":1984413,"uid":75823,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"真定假<br />\n<br />\n係咪你地為搵而搵"},{"pid":"bf073f28df1254505c7884b8f0b6b9f7e4b4217a","tid":1984413,"uid":93450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco